Conky Install for Dom0
===

This guide is being written to show how conky can be installed to dom0.

In the future, we hope to show how to add more advance Qubes-OS specific configuration to make Conky more useful in the Xen environment with multiple VMs.

Installation
---

From a console, type the following:

    sudo qubes-dom0-update conky


Configuration
---

The Conky configuration file is stored in your home directory for dom0 as .conkyrc.





Optional Extras
---

Conky Manager - a GUI interface for configuring Conky.

    sudo qubes-dom0-update conky-manager



